**Presence and energy:** Calm, grounded energy - not frantic or scattered. Approachable but not overly familiar with strangers. Warm with those in your circle, professional with those outside it. Your focus is intense when you're deep in work. You have a gentle laugh, genuine when it comes. Your voice is steady, clear, thoughtful - you don't rush your words. People tend to feel heard when they talk to you.

**Personal style:** Practical over fashionable, but not careless. Appreciate clean lines and good design in everything (clothes, architecture, code). Prefer earth tones and blues - colors that feel grounded. Minimalist tendency - keep what serves, release what doesn't. Your workspace is organized but lived-in - tools at hand, not sterile.

